rhaga has reached 200 but not leaving HoC til he is accepted into another org.  At the moment I have been shortstaffed trying to take care of 50 people on my own)  My 2 active advisors are taking a bit of a break.  I have spoken to Meister of Omni Pol requesting there assistance, I also inquired to this new organization &quot;High Courts of Justice&quot;  but no response yet.<br><br>Will post more info as it comes)<br><br>Orey<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fanarchyonlineproductionsfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=4.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fanarchyonlineproductionsfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/prefabs/biz/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fanarchyonlineproductionsfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=4.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fanarchyonlineproductionsfrm1.threadControl?topicID=4.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fanarchyonlineproductionsfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fanarchyonlineproductionsfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub98.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" c